{"tid":1919090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢29日起直飛多地航班開放訂票　包括4月1日飛香港","createTime":"2020-03-10T14:06:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T01:14:05.000Z","uid":209657,"like":8,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"d342cb31728009d245fde245b6b2d7c03c7d769b","tid":1919090,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:06:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/20200310/314107667251597312.jpeg/xWwAlNwOVvaNlHf68vk6BDapjL9QctXO-LvbMfi72zE?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F20200310%2F314107667251597312.jpeg%2FxWwAlNwOVvaNlHf68vk6BDapjL9QctXO-LvbMfi72zE%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=26e3a4b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n武漢肺炎疫情持續，內地疫情最嚴重的武漢市自1月23日起實行封城管理，至今仍未解除。不過，攜程、途牛、航旅縱橫等內地多間網上訂票平台上，出現了自3月29日起武漢直飛上海、大連、濟南、廈門等內地多地的航班資訊。4月1日起亦有直飛香港的航班，由國泰港龍航空承運（中國國航代碼共享）。"},{"pid":"6f265a1011f878afe2ee91b26a69f786caa05865","tid":1919090,"uid":209657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:08:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/20200310/314104645037461504.jpeg/M2TdsjYpfhGsyeCvWCT3hLlr-9Voo4iCmNhW0pjYVtI\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F20200310%2F314104645037461504.jpeg%2FM2TdsjYpfhGsyeCvWCT3hLlr-9Voo4iCmNhW0pjYVtI&h=74795286&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n記者在內地攜程網查詢發現，截至下午5時，3月29日至4月3日武漢直飛上海航班均顯示無資訊或「已售完」的狀態，但4月4日起的航班就仍然處於售票狀態，直飛價格1890至2300港元不等。"},{"pid":"4d71cdd709f83db75a33df0da4b603c74da6349b","tid":1919090,"uid":209657,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:09:52.000Z","msg":"此外，記者還發現，武漢從3月29日起直飛雲南昆明，遼寧大連，山東的濟南、青島、煙台，貴州貴陽，福建廈門和海南海口等全國多地的航班，目前皆已開放購票。雖然未有直飛北京、廣東省等地的航班，但就提供多個經以上直航點轉機的航程。<br />\n<br />\n至於4月1日起亦有直飛香港的航班，由國泰港龍航空承運，中國國際航空代碼共享，當日售價3000元左右起。武漢飛往澳門、台灣及海外其他城市，就暫未有直航航班提供，旅客亦可購買轉機航程。<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/20200310/314108283789119489.jpeg/klGdl0PmWPf9uqyKCTup5TPYPJpLYZA5MrijBzK4owc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F20200310%2F314108283789119489.jpeg%2FklGdl0PmWPf9uqyKCTup5TPYPJpLYZA5MrijBzK4owc&h=79f4e674&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"979b88903f5ea3ba4fa6940795cc26475d2c12a4","tid":1919090,"uid":128117,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:09:58.000Z","msg":"打尻完意大利要返返黎打香港"},{"pid":"580fc37ae708095ae603a8d37085d42e7ff7930d","tid":1919090,"uid":118120,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:10:44.000Z","msg":"中國正式官方輸出病毒"},{"pid":"7b9efdb21a29d5b271e7dd91039694c9183cee04","tid":1919090,"uid":123774,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:11:44.000Z","msg":"見一個燒一個"},{"pid":"bac343fe8e214344ac8b5b0bd103d2c2bf15c089","tid":1919090,"uid":331861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:11:52.000Z","msg":"4月1愚人節"},{"pid":"df63904ef09c63bef9dd501d09ca21ba8446ab23","tid":1919090,"uid":284855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:11:52.000Z","msg":"即3月31日抗疫成功，世人要多謝共產党<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee1f9340de7c3550fa056c392140d33dd8a5df1c","tid":1919090,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:12:29.000Z","msg":"CX: fat fat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a9df99dd07c33d24fb2420f084fe4191c3a377","tid":1919090,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:12:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6dh2osb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6dh2osb.gif&h=8466655a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"61bc1a9172ab158881b4e9029bf156540e2aa9e3","tid":1919090,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:13:11.000Z","msg":"放左隻野出去就突然無曬事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依個生化戰就係咁開打"},{"pid":"616f9382a9db41eb96d6e28a64b5197086410df3","tid":1919090,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:13:50.000Z","msg":"攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c43d7aa9044acd6b3f01c8b4cbce8600fc43e03","tid":1919090,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:20:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9db526a14435cbfa11db7e5802c70104178222e1","tid":1919090,"uid":221346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:21:02.000Z","msg":"去你老母"},{"pid":"83fc54b3008e51a8ce9253bf1d25b4033660bb30","tid":1919090,"uid":225798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:34:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9878a1b0aad76d8a217c17ed762532e1bf1a8da4","tid":1919090,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:48:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8f8587005b5005b7a7b85a8d57f6593d5e8ff9a","tid":1919090,"uid":218731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:49:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" clas